(8, 'Billionaire cryptocurrency pioneer Brock Pierce says he decided to run for president', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">&ldquo;This </span></span></u></strong><strong><em><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:red\">Cryptocurrency Billionaire Wants to be President</span></span></u></em></strong><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">&rdquo;</span></span></u></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Brock Pierce, this </span></span><strong><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:red\">cryptocurrency billionaire wants to be president</span></span></em></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">since he is &quot;profoundly worried about the condition of our country, our future.&quot;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Brock Pierce, the magnificent personality is the pioneering tycoon of digital currency.&nbsp; Moreover, this personality poses versatile talents. Step by step he climbed the ladder of dominant success. From a child actor, he turned into an entrepreneur. After acquiring prominent entrepreneurship now, he wants to be nominated for presidentship. Brock Pierce made the main significant commercial center for virtual merchandise in web-based gaming, which is relied upon to develop to $190B by 2025. Cryptocurrency business visionary partook as an independent candidate in the presidential race for the 2020 elections.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">In the presidential nomination declaration video (2020), Brock Pierce clarifies that he is a &quot;lifelong fan of business visionaries and private companies, he comprehends the stuff to manufacture a business from the beginning&rdquo;.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">The U.S. presidential candidate showed involvement in discussions regarding Covid-19 and protests held in different cities all over the country. Brock Pierce demands Americans come together and loud slogans such as &quot;We are all in this together, and Cast the vote.&quot;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><img alt=\"https://docs.google.com/drawings/u/0/d/sZ_LVB-1gGD_DDY4jSKngfA/image?w=312&amp;h=204&amp;rev=1&amp;ac=1&amp;parent=12OQ9Vh-RGb0NAhqTn58Cw0WUy5JrAry-\" src=\"https://docs.google.com/drawings/u/0/d/sZ_LVB-1gGD_DDY4jSKngfA/image?w=312&amp;h=204&amp;rev=1&amp;ac=1&amp;parent=12OQ9Vh-RGb0NAhqTn58Cw0WUy5JrAry-\" style=\"float:right; height:204px; padding:15px; width:312px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Further showing fascination towards the nation&#39;s future, Pierce includes that Americans need to get a handle on a future stacked up with inventive degrees of progress and he can help the country in dealings associated with 21st-century innovation practices.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">He&#39;s completely ready for the extraordinary scrutiny he will encounter as the political race approaches.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">He demonstrated stress over the nation&#39;s future and said that he is seeing the country is plunging with bunches of polarization. The country is ceaselessly captivating in good and bad times. There isn&#39;t sufficient moderate assessment to unite us. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">He intends to design a phase in great part through publicly supporting residents on his site, which is additionally looking for donations.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Moreover, Pierce illustrated, by employing his expertise in a private company and digital currency, he will participate as a moderate independent who will grasp innovation to prod development.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><img alt=\"https://docs.google.com/drawings/u/0/d/srP_23e7eg1JJveNNYIxAmw/image?w=469&amp;h=339&amp;rev=1&amp;ac=1&amp;parent=12OQ9Vh-RGb0NAhqTn58Cw0WUy5JrAry-\" src=\"https://docs.google.com/drawings/u/0/d/srP_23e7eg1JJveNNYIxAmw/image?w=469&amp;h=339&amp;rev=1&amp;ac=1&amp;parent=12OQ9Vh-RGb0NAhqTn58Cw0WUy5JrAry-\" style=\"float:right; height:339px; width:469px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">When the news of Pierce&rdquo; This </span></span><strong><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:red\">Cryptocurrency Billionaire Wants to be President</span></span></em></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">&rdquo; was spreading like a fire, meanwhile an event happened. The unexpected application of Pierce concurs with Kanye West&#39;s offer for the White House, which Pierce embraced excitedly as a way to prod the collaboration of millennials. Pierce felt truly energized.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Ideally, all things considered, we can convey a ground-breaking message to American individuals.&quot; Pierce stated.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">He is a private venture business person and has a good idea that how enormous things are made from nothing. He claimed that a genuine business person can fabricate the country and just trailblazers and business people can get us out of the current circumstance.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Billionaire cryptocurrency pioneer Brock Pierce says he decided to run for president', 'Brock Pierce, this cryptocurrency billionaire wants to be president since he is &quot;profoundly worried about the condition of our country, our future.&quot;', 'New', NULL, '341464286.jpg', 'billionaire-cryptocurrency-pioneer-brock-pierce-says-he-decided-to-run-for-president', 'Monday-15-03-21', 'cryptoinject.com', 'cryptocurrency pioneer, Brock Pierce, run for president, cryptocurrency, billionaire, wants to be, president', 'New', 'publish'),
